text:
Orchard Park, N.Y. â€” The Seattle Seahawks are a 4.5-point favorite against the San Francisco 49ers on Thursday night.
The Seahawks (2-4) have lost close games to the Cincinnati Bengals and Carolina Panthers the past two weeks. The 49ers (2-4) broke a four-game losing streak by beating the Baltimore Ravens on Sunday.
The Buffalo Bills are a 5.5-point favorite for their game against the Jacksonville Jaguars on Sunday in London.
